(2214, 77, 'Occupation', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/bcf8f332-c7e1-4a08-8651-28d668290eaf', 'metallurgist', 'consultant metallurgist\nchemical tester\nchemical technician\nextraction metallurgist\nforging engineer\nmetallurgist\nsteel industry experts\nphysical metallurgist', '', 'released', '2017-02-10 17:54:39', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/regulated-professions/unregulated', '', '', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/member-occupations,\nhttp://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/occupations', 'Metallurgists specialise in the extraction and processing of metals such as iron, steel, zinc, copper and aluminium. They work to mold or combine both pure and mixed metals (alloys) into new shapes and properties. Metallurgists handle the extraction of metal ores and develop their use in metal processing techniques. They may work in both manufacturing or do scientific research about the performance of metals.', '2146.5'),
(2215, 78, 'Occupation', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/c4071145-a774-4cf4-aefa-ae18a385cca4', 'logistics engineer', 'logistics engineering consultant\nlogistics technology engineer\nlogistics technology engineering expert\nlogistics engineering adviser\nlogistics technology engineering consultant\nlogistics technology engineering specialist\nlogistics engineering specialist\nlogistics technology engineering adviser\nlogistic engineer\nlogistics engineering expert', '', 'released', '2016-07-05 16:19:37', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/regulated-professions/unregulated', '', '', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/occupations,\nhttp://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/member-occupations', 'Logistics engineers design and implement systems aimed to optimise the time and efforts invested in transportation activities. They ensure that systems allow for micro-tracking and smooth communication across transport methods and stages.', '2149.2.6'),
(2216, 78, 'Occupation', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/c8fa93eb-7c2c-42c3-b135-c2e825a6615e', 'test engineer', 'agricultural equipment test engineer', '', 'released', '2017-01-27 10:59:34', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/regulated-professions/unregulated', '', '', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/occupations,\nhttp://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/member-occupations', 'Test engineers plan and perform detailed quality tests during', '2149.14'),
(2217, 82, 'Occupation', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/c5d36eef-df20-47a8-a332-5b4358fa83e3', 'telecommunications analyst', 'telecommunications consultant\ntelecom analyst\ntelecoms analysts\ncommunication analyst\ncommunications analyst\ntelecommunications analysts\nnetwork planner', '', 'released', '2017-01-17 13:42:15', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/regulated-professions/unregulated', 'Excludes people performing telecommunication design activities.', '', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/occupations,\nhttp://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/member-occupations', 'Telecommunications analysts review, analyse and evaluate an organisation\'s telecommunications needs and systems. They provide training on the telecommunications system features and functionalities.', '2153.1.1'),
(2218, 86, 'Occupation', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/bc4d1659-6860-488e-bc13-e87eb0e36f67', 'furniture designer', 'furniture craftswoman\nfurniture design advisor\nfurniture artist\nfurniture planner & designer\nproduct designer, furniture\nfurniture designer and maker\nhand-made furniture builder\nfurniture craftsman\nfurniture technologist\nfurniture designers\nfurniture technician\nhand-made furniture maker\nfurniture planner and designer\ninterior and furniture designer\nfurniture & interior designer\nfurniture designer and planner\nfurniture designer & planner\nfurniture planner\ninterior FF&E designer\nfurniture maker\nfurniture builder\nfurniture designer & maker\ninterior & furniture designer\nfurniture design specialist\nfurniture design consultant\nFF&E designer\nfurniture design expert\nfurniture, fixments, and equipment designer\nhand-made furniture designer\nfurniture and interior designer', '', 'released', '2016-07-05 16:17:46', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/regulated-professions/unregulated', '', '', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/occupations,\nhttp://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/member-occupations', 'Furniture designers work on items of furniture and related products. They design the product and are involved in its production as craftsmen and designers or makers. The conception of furniture combines innovative design, functional requirements and aesthetic appeal.', '2163.1.4'),
(2219, 89, 'Occupation', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/bab5fa79-7f96-4e21-87b6-1eba560b8d9a', '3D modeller', '3D modellers\n3D texturing artist\nCGI modeller\ncomputer-generated imagery modeller\n3D artist\n3D developer\n3D specialist', '', 'released', '2017-02-02 13:26:10', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/regulated-professions/unregulated', 'Excludes people performing managerial activities.', '', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/member-occupations,\nhttp://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/occupations', '3D modellers design 3D models of objects, virtual environments, layouts, characters, and 3D virtual animated agents.', '2166.1'),
(2220, 89, 'Occupation', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/c995fe34-0909-4ce3-b7b7-97945efede56', 'video designer', 'projection & video designer\ngraphics and video designer\nvideo & graphics designer\nvideo and projection designer\nvisual designer\nprojection designer\nprojection and video designer\ngraphics & video designer\nvideo & projection designer\nvideo and graphics designer\nvideo jockey', '', 'released', '2016-12-20 12:15:51', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/regulated-professions/unregulated', 'This', '', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/occupations,\nhttp://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/member-occupations', 'Video designers develop a projected image design concept for a performance and supervise the execution of it. Their work is based on research and artistic vision. Their design is influenced by and influences other designs and must be conform with these designs and the overall artistic vision. Therefore, the designers work closely with artistic directors, operators and the artistic team. Video designers prepare media fragments to be used in a performance, which can involve recording, composing, manipulating and editing. During rehearsals and performance they coach the operators to obtain optimal timing and manipulation. Video ', '2166.14'),
(2221, 89, 'Occupation', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/cb93fd23-1f51-4495-867a-936c1967066b', 'art director', 'advertising art director\ncreative director\nvisual art director\ndesigner\nartistic projects manager\nmaestro\nstage director', '', 'released', '2017-02-23 12:37:44', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/regulated-professions/unregulated', '', '', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/occupations,\nhttp://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/member-occupations', 'Art directors shape the visual layout of a concept. They create innovative designs, develop artistic projects ', '2166.4'),
(2222, 98, 'Occupation', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/c2a29b8d-1042-4766-a162-e174c7a77421', 'complementary therapist', 'traditional therapist\ntraditional practitioner of natural health\nalternative therapist\nayurveda practitioner\ntherapist in complementary medicine\npractitioner in complementary therapy\nholistic therapist\npractitioner in complementary medicine\nnaturopathic practitioner\nsustainable health practitioner\nnatural medicine therapist\ncomplementary therapy practitioner\nnatural health practitioner\nalternative medicine therapist\nnaturopath\ncomplementary practitioner\nalternative medicine practitioner\ncomplementary medicine practitioner', '', 'released', '2017-02-02 11:39:24', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/regulated-professions/unregulated', 'Includes people performing Acupuncture, Alexander Technique, Aromatherapy, Art therapy, Autogenic training, Ayurveda, Bach Flower Remedies, Balneotherapy, Bioresonance, Bowen therapy Buyteko, Chi Gung, Craniosacral therapy, Cupping, Feldenkreis, Herbalism', '', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/member-occupations,\nhttp://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/occupations', 'Complementary therapists use a range of complementary and alternative therapies to work simultaneously with the clients` body, mind, and spirit in a holistic approach. They offer practices and services for holistic wellbeing, health maintenance, health education, health promotion and prevention of illness, along with the sustainable treatment of certain illnesses, especially chronic illnesses. Their practices include but are not limited to acupuncture, aromatherapy, banotherapy, homeopathy, and herbal medicine.', '2230.1'),
