(2225, 108, 'Occupation', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/c37d0026-989b-4705-9bcb-30cccd8308fa', 'prepared meals nutritionist', '', '', 'released', '2017-02-14 14:48:11', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/regulated-professions/unregulated', '', '', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/member-occupations,\nhttp://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/occupations', 'Prepared meals nutritionists value ingredients, manufacturing processes, and foodstuffs in order to assure nutritional quality and suitability of prepared meals and dishes. They study nutritional value of foodstuffs and dishes and advise on the', '2265.1.1'),
