(2893, 466, 'Occupation', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/f96e3735-405c-4ca9-8a86-d37f64ea7164', 'wind musical instrument maker', 'brass instrument assembler\nwoodwind instrument builder\nwoodwind instrument assembler\nwind musical instrument builder\nbrass instrument craftsman\nbrass instrument builder\nwoodwind instrument craftswoman\nbrass instrument maker\nbrass instrument craftswoman\nwind instrument maker\nwoodwind instrument maker\nwoodwind instrument craftsman', '', 'released', '2016-07-05 17:00:52', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/regulated-professions/unregulated', 'Includes people producing smaller musical instruments or accessories, such as metronomes, tuning forks or musical boxes.', '', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/occupations,\nhttp://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/member-occupations', 'Wind musical instrument makers create and assemble parts to make wind instruments according to specified instructions and diagrams. They measure and cut the tubing for the resonator, assemble parts such as braces, slides, valves, piston, bell heads and mouth pieces, test and inspect the finished instrument.', '7312.7'),
(2894, 467, 'Occupation', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/eb64b583-20fe-467f-8e44-8aae263a0139', 'silversmith', 'silver earrings fabricator\nboutique silversmith\nsilver jewellery maker\nsilversmiths\ntrophy maker\nsilver jewellery fabricator\ntrophy silversmith\nsilver ring fabricator\nsilver earrings maker\nsilver jewel smith\nsilver ring maker', '', 'released', '2016-10-19 14:38:40', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/regulated-professions/unregulated', '', '', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/occupations,\nhttp://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/member-occupations', 'Silversmiths design, manufacture and sell jewelry. They also adjust, repair and appraise gems and jewelry. Silversmiths are specialized in working with silver and other precious metals.', '7313.1.8'),
(2895, 472, 'Occupation', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/ebff4fcf-6b69-4290-a55c-9bfe4cc7a1ef', 'fishing net maker', 'drift net maker\nfisheries net maker\nmaker of fishing nets', '', 'released', '2016-07-05 13:29:39', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/regulated-professions/unregulated', '', '', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/member-occupations,\nhttp://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/occupations', 'Fishing net makers make and assemble fishing net gear and carry out reparation and maintenance, as directed by the drawings and/or traditional methods.', '7318.3'),
(2896, 475, 'Occupation', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/f5596182-70b2-4c18-97ab-f9405bae0385', 'screen making technician', 'silk screen engraver\nrotary engraver\ntextile engraver\nsilk screen etcher\ntextile engravers\ntextile screen maker\netcher and engraver', '', 'released', '2016-10-20 16:44:18', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/regulated-professions/unregulated', '', '', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/occupations,\nhttp://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/member-occupations', 'Screen making technicians engrave or etch screens for textile printing.', '7321.1.5'),
(2897, 476, 'Occupation', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/ea4aff10-4d20-4a2b-886b-299c2bd349f1', 'offset printer', 'newspaper printer\nnewspaper press specialist\noffset pressman\noffset printer operator\noffset press specialist\nlithographic printing technician\nnewspaper press operator\noffset lithography printer\nlithographic printing specialist\noffset printer specialist\noffset press operator\nlithographic printing operator\nnewspaper press technician\noffset press assistant\npad printing machine operator\noffset printer technician\noffset press technician', '', 'released', '2017-01-17 14:42:34', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/regulated-professions/unregulated', '', '', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/occupations,\nhttp://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/member-occupations', 'Offset printers handle an offset press in order to print an image. The offset press transfers an inked image from the plate to a rubber blanket before to print it onto the printing surface.', '7322.5'),
(2898, 480, 'Occupation', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/fddb7bd8-f176-4dc8-9d12-32b6072452c9', 'electric meter technician', 'electricity meter technician\nsmart meter technician\nelectricity meter installer\nelectricity meter installation technician\nelectric meter maintenance operative\nelectric meter test technician\nelectricity meter maintenance worker\nsmart meter installer\nelectricity meter test technician\nelectric meter installer\nelectric meter maintenance worker\nelectric meter installation technician\nelectricity meter maintenance operative', '', 'released', '2016-10-17 18:08:16', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/regulated-professions/unregulated', '', '', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/member-occupations,\nhttp://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/occupations', 'Electric meter technicians install and maintain electric meter systems in facilities or buildings. They install the equipment in accordance with regulations and repair faults and other problems. They test the equipment and advise on the use and care.', '7411.1.2'),
(2899, 481, 'Occupation', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/f4eaff3d-f8d0-4a6a-aa90-76827c0fbada', 'household appliances repair technician', 'washing machine servicer\ndryer repairer\ndishwasher repairer\nhome appliance repairman\nwindow air conditioner repairer\nAC repairer\nrefrigerator repairer\nappliance service technician', '', 'released', '2016-07-05 17:11:15', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/regulated-professions/unregulated', '', '', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/occupations,\nhttp://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/member-occupations', 'Household appliances repair technicians use electrical equipment to test resistance or voltage and to identify appliances\' malfunctions. They repair small and large electrical or gas home appliances such as vacuum cleaners, washing machines, dishwashers, air conditioners and refrigerators.', '7412.5'),
(2900, 481, 'Occupation', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/f8d1bcf9-9ca1-408f-a713-7bdf28c400fd', 'lift engineer', 'lift installation worker\nlift maintenance engineer\nelevator installer\nlift constructor\nelevator service inspector\nelevator erecting mechanic\nelevator installation team member\nelevator builder\nlift construction worker\nelevator service technican\nlift erecting mechanic\nescalator installer\nlift installation team worker\nlift technician\nelevator service mechanic\nlift service mechanic\nlift repair engineer\nelevator maintenance mechanic\nlift builder\nlift installer\nelevator service engineer\nlift repair technician\nlift erector\nelevator constructor\nlift installation team member\nlift service technician\nlift maintenance technician\nlift callout engineer\nlift maintenance mechanic\nlift inspector\nlift service engineer\nelevator engineer\nelevator erector', '', 'released', '2016-11-17 11:41:52', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/regulated-professions/unregulated', 'Includes people working in installation and maintenance of escalators, stair lifts and other electronic transport equipment.', '', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/member-occupations,\nhttp://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/occupations', 'Lift engineers set lifts into a prepared framed hoistway. They install support assembly, set up the lift pump or motor, piston or cable, and mechanism.', '7412.6'),
(2901, 481, 'Occupation', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/fd86ebe1-bad4-4486-9b76-01a48030e49a', 'rolling stock electrician', 'electrical train electrician\nmultiple unit builder\ncarriage builder\ndepot electrician\nrail depot electrician\nrail electrician\nrailcar electrician\nrail vehicle electrician\nlocomotive electrician\nrailway vehicle builder\nrail workshop engineering technician\nrolling stock builder\nrailcar builder\nrailway depot electrician\ncarriage electrician\nrail vehicle builder\nmultiple unit electrician\nwagon builder\nrailway vehicle electrician\nlocomotive builder\nrailway workshop engineering technician\nwagon electrician\nworkshop engineering technician\nrailway electrician', '', 'released', '2017-01-17 13:53:12', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/regulated-professions/unregulated', '', '', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/occupations,\nhttp://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/member-occupations', 'Rolling stock electricians install, maintain and repair electrical and electronic systems in rail vehicles such as air conditioning systems, lamps, heating systems, electrical wiring etc. They use diagnostic testing equipment to inspect vehicles and find faults. To do repair work, they use hand tools and specialised electrical instruments and machines.', '7412.11'),
(2902, 482, 'Occupation', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/f2ee2cda-9d02-49c3-8280-da5892d0055b', 'street lighting electrician', 'highway lights operative\nstreet lighting repair electrician\nstreet lighting installation electrician\nstreet light electrician\nstreet light repair electrician\nhighway lighting repair electrician\nhighway lighting operative\nstreet lighting operative\nstreet light operative\nhighway lighting installation electrician', '', 'released', '2017-01-17 11:59:13', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/regulated-professions/unregulated', '', '', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/member-occupations,\nhttp://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/occupations', 'Street lighting electricians construct and maintain electric power transmission and distribution in street lights. They maintain, test and repair street lights in compliance with safety regulations.', '7413.1.3'),
(2903, 484, 'Occupation', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/ecdc43f5-3b32-4f94-abf8-cd46480c8cb8', 'vehicle electronics installer', 'vehicle electronics repairer\nmotor vehicle technician, auto electronics\nvehicle electronic installation technician\nvehicle electronics technician\nmotor vehicle electronics technician\nmotor vehicle technician (auto electronics)\nauto electronic technician\nelectronic installation technician\nauto technician\nautoelectronic technician', '', 'released', '2017-01-26 11:24:18', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/regulated-professions/unregulated', 'Excludes <a resource=\"http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/6656337f-67eb-4f48-b1e4-ecccdfa44dd2\" typeOf=\"http://data.europa.eu/esco/model#Occupation\" href=\"http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/6656337f-67eb-4f48-b1e4-ecccdfa44dd2\"><span property=\"http:/', '', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/occupations,\nhttp://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/member-occupations', 'Vehicle electronics installers set up equipment and accessories in motor vehicles such as CD players and GPS. They use', '7421.7'),
(2904, 484, 'Occupation', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/f8ab2e08-d14e-4938-a2cd-c04821556db7', 'consumer electronics repair technician', 'repairer\nconsumer electronics technician\nelectronics repairer\nrepairman\ntrouble-shooter\nconsumer electronics repairman\nconsumer\ntechnician', '', 'released', '2016-07-05 17:09:27', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/regulated-professions/unregulated', '', '', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/member-occupations,\nhttp://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/occupations', 'Consumer electronics repair technicians use electrical equipment to diagnose malfunctions and test functionality of consumer electronics such as TVs, video and audio systems and digital cameras. They read manufacturers\' instructions and conduct the necessary repairs or replacements.', '7421.3'),
(2905, 485, 'Occupation', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/f0f6d531-eb96-4bad-84ff-8e2999ea68e6', 'mobile phone repair technician', 'hand held phone technician\ncell phone technician\ncellullar phone technician\nmobile phone repairer\nLCD technician\ncommunication equipment repair technician\nmobile phone repairman', '', 'released', '2016-07-05 17:11:40', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/regulated-professions/unregulated', '', '', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/member-occupations,\nhttp://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/occupations', 'Mobile phone repair technicians run tests to assess the mobile phones\' functionality, install and update phone software, troubleshoot wiring problems, and replace damaged parts and components such as batteries, LCD screens, keypads, buttons. They also advise their clients on warranty issues and recommend products based on their expertise.', '7422.3.1'),
(2906, 488, 'Occupation', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/f1783e61-38b7-468e-b495-9c3c92f5ab0d', 'halal slaughterer', 'halal slaughterperson\nhalal method slaughterer\nhalal slaughterman\nhalal slaughterwoman\nslaughterer following halal method', '', 'released', '2017-01-17 14:43:29', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/regulated-professions/unregulated', '', '', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/occupations,\nhttp://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/member-occupations', 'Halal slaughterers slaughter animals and process carcasses of halal meat from cows and chickens for further processing and distribution. They slaughter animals as stated in Islamic law and ensure that the animals are fed, slaughtered and hung up accordingly.', '7511.6.1'),
(2907, 489, 'Occupation', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/ff42d44c-34f8-46be-ad3a-2aad9a5e43f0', 'pastry maker', 'pastry production operator\npastry cook\npastry production worker', '', 'released', '2020-06-11 14:49:14', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/regulated-professions/unregulated', '', '', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/occupations,\nhttp://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/member-occupations', 'Pastry makers prepare and bake cakes, cookies, croissants, pies and alike', '7512.5'),
(2908, 496, 'Occupation', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/fb6df00f-4810-442b-8f93-89b9580c7c9f', 'furniture finisher', 'furniture finishing worker\nfurniture finishing operative\nwooden furniture finisher\nfurniture stainer\nfurniture machine finisher\nfurniture painter\nfurniture varnisher\nfurniture polisher\nwooden furniture production worker\nfurniture finishing technician\nwood furniture varnisher\nfurniture sander\nwooden furniture varnisher\nfurniture hand finisher\nwood furniture painter\nwooden furniture painter\nwooden furniture stainer\nFrench polisher\nwood furniture stainer\nwooden furniture production operative\nwooden furniture sander\nfurniture sprayer\nwood furniture finisher\nwooden furniture polisher\nwood furniture sprayer', '', 'released', '2016-12-20 11:08:45', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/regulated-professions/unregulated', '', '', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/occupations,\nhttp://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/member-occupations', 'Furniture finishers treat the surface of wood furniture using hand and power tools to sand, clean and polish. They apply wood coatings onto wooden surfaces by using different techniques such as brushing or using a spray gun. They choose and apply the right coatings with protective and/or decorative purposes.', '7522.5'),
(2909, 499, 'Occupation', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/fd1c0f5a-f465-4067-af54-621e68c90f74', 'milliner', 'hat maker\ncustom headwear manufacturer\nhatter\nheadwear manufacturer\nheadgear manufacturer', '', 'released', '2016-07-05 17:00:44', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/regulated-professions/unregulated', '', '', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/occupations,\nhttp://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/member-occupations', 'Milliners design and manufacture hats and other headwear.', '7531.4'),
(2910, 504, 'Occupation', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/f8e76759-811e-4b39-9adf-3e77429cff8f', 'shoemaker', 'custom shoemaker\nhand craft shoe maker\nshoe repairer\ncobbler\ntraditional shoe manufacturer', '', 'released', '2017-01-17 13:48:42', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/regulated-professions/unregulated', '', '', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/member-occupations,\nhttp://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/occupations', 'Shoemakers use hand or machine operations for traditional manufacturing of a various range of footwear. They also repair all types of footwear in a repair shop.', '7536.2'),
(2911, 522, 'Occupation', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/ee37a4a5-5360-4e94-a749-a2b8ead08500', 'tracer powder blender', 'flammable chemical mixer\ntracer-powder blender\nigniter powder mixer\ntracer powder maker\nflammable chemical blender\nigniter powder blender\ntracer powder mixer', '', 'released', '2016-10-20 14:58:06', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/regulated-professions/unregulated', '', '', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/member-occupations,\nhttp://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/occupations', 'Tracer powder blenders operate machines and equipment used to create igniters and tracer powders, by mixing liquid and dry chemicals, making sure the required parameters are set and that the flammable mixtures are according to specifications.', '8131.2.5'),
(2912, 522, 'Occupation', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/ff5210a5-2ea9-43b4-bebc-8d565f928eaa', 'cosmetics production machine operator', 'cosmetics production machine tender\ncosmetics production machine worker\ncosmetics production operative\ncosmetics factory worker\ncosmetics production operator\ncosmetics plant worker\ncosmetics production worker\ncosmetics production machine operative', '', 'released', '2017-01-17 11:56:58', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/regulated-professions/unregulated', '', '', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/member-occupations,\nhttp://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/occupations', 'Cosmetics production machine operators tend machinery for the manufacturing of cosmetic products by setting up the machines and tools, cleaning and maintaining the equipment and abiding by the production schedule.', '8131.4'),
(2913, 525, 'Occupation', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/fcab4bb1-c05b-43e3-98d8-f60b13c152f2', 'coagulation operator', 'latex coagulation worker\nrubber production process machine worker\nrubber production process machine operative\ncoagulation operative\nlatex coagulation operator\nlatex coagulation operative\nrubber coagulation operative\nrubber production process machine operator\nrubber coagulation operator\nrubber coagulation worker\ncoagulation worker\nrubber production process operator', '', 'released', '2016-10-20 17:25:39', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/regulated-professions/unregulated', '', '', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/member-occupations,\nhttp://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/occupations', 'Coagulation operators control machines to coagulate synthetic rubber latex into rubber crumb slurry. They prepare these rubber crumbs for finishing processes. Coagulation operators examine the appearance of the crumbs and adjust the operation of filters, shaker screens and hammer mills to remove moisture from the rubber crumbs.', '8141.1.2'),
(2914, 526, 'Occupation', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/occupation/ec238461-93b6-4516-a251-52d1153b53ac', 'compression moulding machine operator', 'compression molding machine operative\ncompression moulding machine operative\nmoulding machine setter\nmolding machine setter\ncompression molding machine operator\nproduction operative (plastic moulding)\nproduction operator (plastic moulding)\ncompression molding machine setter\nmoulding machine operative\nmolding machine operative\ncompression moulding machine setter', '', 'released', '2016-07-05 16:51:59', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/regulated-professions/unregulated', '', '', 'http://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/occupations,\nhttp://data.europa.eu/esco/concept-scheme/member-occupations', 'Compression moulding machine operators set up and operate machines to mould plastic products, according to requirements. They select and install dies on press. Compression moulding machine operators weigh the amount of premixed compound needed and pour it into the die well. They regulate the temperature of dies.', '8142.3'),
